{"tid":1616343,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府疑遺失萬二份派四千元申請表","createTime":"2019-10-03T11:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T14:34:26.000Z","uid":187876,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"96178145959ebe073a46b49033272fd773e8a63d","tid":1616343,"uid":187876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:27:08.000Z","msg":"政府懷疑遺失一萬二千份派發四千元的申請表，已經重新檢視所管有的表格，若未能尋回會通報私隱專員公署，公署就指已收到職津處備案。<br />\n<br />\n職津處指出，有一萬二千份關愛共享計劃的申請輸入初步資料，即已確認收妥，但可能因為夾雜在其他已處理的申請表中，未能尋回，暫時未能繼續審批。為加快完成處理這些個案，職津處已發出電話短訊聯絡有關申請人，亦會重新檢視所有表格。如果未能尋回，會與受影響的申請人另作跟進，並通報私隱專員公署。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n職津處又表示至今已處理約三百四十萬份申請、即約 98% 。而在三百萬份獲批申請中， 99% 已獲批共 106 億元款項。正積極跟進處理六萬多份未完成審批的申請，當中五萬多份是申請人未能提供足夠資料作查核，已聯絡他們請他們盡快提交。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n私隱專員公署表示，已收到職津處就未能尋回部分申請表備案，在確認資料外洩前，可先在合理時間內進行內部查找，如最後證實遺失，公署會展開循規審查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/558407/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%96%91%E9%81%BA%E5%A4%B1%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%8C%E4%BB%BD%E6%B4%BE%E5%9B%9B%E5%8D%83%E5%85%83%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%A1%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F558407%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%2581%25BA%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%2585%2583%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25A1%25A8&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEvsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=e7d42e42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F558407%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%2581%25BA%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%2585%2583%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25A1%25A8&h=5d55bce1\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/558407/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%96%91%E9%81%BA%E5%A4%B1%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%8C%E4%BB%BD%E6%B4%BE%E5%9B%9B%E5%8D%83%E5%85%83%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%A1%A8</a>"},{"pid":"fcb3651ce7a90091e4d334b2dbcea0cc110dc8eb","tid":1616343,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea571b01c56b99387a15510fdaef7e3d9c8d7ccd","tid":1616343,"uid":57738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:28:15.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"1df45a141b046ae273c0d8b48f9fcea92e6de9d1","tid":1616343,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:29:45.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n <code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"f3da06c92a614dd0ab4a25dd3b47b01c3acf169a","tid":1616343,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:34:26.000Z","msg":"派錢都搞唔掂"}]}